OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA fine day with plenty of
OL,6,Fsunshine, though locally hazy at
OL,7,Ftimes. Hot or very hot during the
OL,8,Fafternoon, with light winds offering
OL,9,Flittle relief from the heat. Coastal
OL,10,Fareas will remain cooler as an onshore
OL,11,Fbreeze develops.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAnother warm night for many,
OL,14,Fespecially in urban areas and cities,
OL,15,Fwhile rural locations become
OL,16,Fnoticeably cooler. Dry with light
OL,17,Fwinds and largely clear skies
OL,18,Fthroughout.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
