OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FAnother hot day, with daytime
OL,6,Ftemperatures widely above average. Dry
OL,7,Fand predominantly sunny. Cooler along
OL,8,Fcoastal areas, with an onshore breeze.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry
OL,11,Fand largely sunny, though cooler, on
OL,12,FSaturday. Low cloud and patchy drizzle
OL,13,Fpossible early Sunday before brighter
OL,14,Fconditions develop. Dry with plenty of
OL,15,Fsunshine on Monday, though turning
OL,16,Fcooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
